WITH OldestFemaleClients AS (
    SELECT c.client_id, c.district_id, a.account_id
    FROM client c
    JOIN disp d ON c.client_id = d.client_id
    JOIN account a ON d.account_id = a.account_id
    WHERE c.gender = 'F' AND c.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client WHERE gender = 'F')
),
DistrictAverageSalaries AS (
    SELECT d.district_id, AVG(d.A12) AS avg_salary
    FROM district d
    GROUP BY d.district_id
),
SalaryGap AS (
    SELECT MAX(avg_salary) - MIN(avg_salary) AS salary_gap
    FROM DistrictAverageSalaries
)
SELECT o.account_id, sg.salary_gap
FROM OldestFemaleClients o
JOIN DistrictAverageSalaries das ON o.district_id = das.district_id
JOIN SalaryGap sg ON 1=1
WHERE das.avg_salary = (SELECT MIN(avg_salary) FROM DistrictAverageSalaries);	----- bird -----	financial

SELECT a.account_id, l.amount
FROM loan l
JOIN account a ON l.account_id = a.account_id
WHERE l.duration > 12 AND l.status = 'A' AND a.date LIKE '1993%'
ORDER BY l.amount DESC
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	financial
